headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Running Back (Remix)
content:
This week marks the return of three action-packed multiplayer modes, each delivering a unique and distinct flavor of whiplash: Hunting Pack (Remix), Running Back (Remix), and Hippy Hunting.

Few traditions are as American as Running Back (Remix): a nimble Runner behind the wheel of a pint-sized Panto must face down a squad of imposing Tezeracts to reach the opposing teamâ€™s end zone. Win or lose, both sides will earn Double Rewards, all week long. Ready? Break.
